---
By: Eliphas Levi
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 154
    Verse: 12
Tags:
  - Falsehood
---
Truth is the day of soul, and the night is falsehood. All truth implies
falsehood because forms are limited, and all falsehood implies and
necessitates a truth in the rectification of the finite by the infinite.
